62 0 obj
<</Dest[690 0 R/XYZ 33 79 0]/Parent 57 0 R/Prev 63 0 R/Title(3.1.4 Information Systems Assets must have a defined lifecycle and process for that lifecycle - acquisition to disposal. For example, employee-assigned Information System Assets must be returned to Adobe IT at the end of useful life, or upon an employ...)>>
endobj
63 0 obj
